au.org.massive.strudel_web

Class Settings

  • java.lang.Object
    • au.org.massive.strudel_web.Settings

  • public class Settings
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides settings for the application. Requires "strudel-web.properties" to be in the class path. Settings objects are singletons, and configuration is loaded only once.
    Author:
    jrigby
